{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/21-lru-cache/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"20bb8c01-835e-5400-a0f4-2042fe9161c8","excerpt":"밀렸던거 다풀라니까 마음이 안따라줘서 쉽지가 않네 😋. \n어제의 두번째 문제는 Least Recently Used (LRU) cache 문제였다. 어디서 많이 봤다~ 싶었는데 운영체제에서 배웠었다 ㅋㅋㅋ 운체 ㅜㅜ 짱싫어했었다… 지금처럼 공부했으면 참 좋았을텐데!란 갑분 아쉬움이 남는 문제.  문제 요약 Least Recently Used(LRU) 알고리즘을 구현하는 문제\n근데!!! 😎 LRU…","html":"<p>밀렸던거 다풀라니까 마음이 안따라줘서 쉽지가 않네 😋.\n어제의 두번째 <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/lru-cache/\">문제</a>는 <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cache_replacement_policies#LRU\">Least Recently Used (LRU) cache</a> 문제였다. 어디서 많이 봤다~ 싶었는데 운영체제에서 배웠었다 ㅋㅋㅋ 운체 ㅜㅜ 짱싫어했었다… 지금처럼 공부했으면 참 좋았을텐데!란 갑분 아쉬움이 남는 문제.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"lru-cache\"\n        title=\"lru-cache\"\n        src=\"/static/d86d75aec13e1bf188675671968a25f5/e5166/lru-cache.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d86d75aec13e1bf188675671968a25f5/f93b5/lru-cache.jpg 300w,\n/static/d86d75aec13e1bf188675671968a25f5/b4294/lru-cache.jpg 600w,\n/static/d86d75aec13e1bf188675671968a25f5/e5166/lru-cache.jpg 1200w,\n/static/d86d75aec13e1bf188675671968a25f5/5df6d/lru-cache.jpg 1482w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>Least Recently Used(LRU) 알고리즘을 구현하는 문제\n근데!!! 😎 LRU가 뭔질 알아야 문제를 풀지;;;</p>\n<p>그래서 이것저것 유투브에 찾아봤는데 <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S6IfqDXWa10\">이 영상</a>이 도움이 많이 되었다.\n예제를 잘 보면 <code class=\"language-text\">put</code>과 <code class=\"language-text\">get</code>이 나온다. 간단히 요약하면 <code class=\"language-text\">put</code>은 메모리에 할당하는 것이고, <code class=\"language-text\">get</code>은 이미 메모리에 할당되있는 값을 반환하는 것이다.\n조금 더 자세히 어떻게 구현할지 알아보자. </p>\n<h2 id=\"0-자료구조는-queue\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#0-%EC%9E%90%EB%A3%8C%EA%B5%AC%EC%A1%B0%EB%8A%94-queue\" aria-label=\"0 자료구조는 queue permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>0. 자료구조는? queue</h2>\n<p>queue를 사용해서 구현하면 쉽다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.666666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"queue\"\n        title=\"queue\"\n        src=\"/static/63bbf0fbd1c41bef7c7aa0da7ad2caa9/c1b63/lru-cache-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/63bbf0fbd1c41bef7c7aa0da7ad2caa9/5a46d/lru-cache-3.png 300w,\n/static/63bbf0fbd1c41bef7c7aa0da7ad2caa9/0a47e/lru-cache-3.png 600w,\n/static/63bbf0fbd1c41bef7c7aa0da7ad2caa9/c1b63/lru-cache-3.png 1200w,\n/static/63bbf0fbd1c41bef7c7aa0da7ad2caa9/d61c2/lru-cache-3.png 1800w,\n/static/63bbf0fbd1c41bef7c7aa0da7ad2caa9/29beb/lru-cache-3.png 1830w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"1-put\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-put\" aria-label=\"1 put permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. put</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">put</code>을 할 때, 이미 메모리가 꽉 차있는 경우에는 가장 최근에 사용안했던 부분을 제거하고 새로운 메모리를 할당하는 것이다. 근데 새로운 메모리를 할당한다는 것은 가장 최근에 사용한 의미가 아닌가? 그래서 가장 앞쪽으로 위치해주는 작업을 함께 해주어야한다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 122%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"put\"\n        title=\"put\"\n        src=\"/static/9d3ffadb4693960fa53446e9492efb91/00d43/lru-cache-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9d3ffadb4693960fa53446e9492efb91/5a46d/lru-cache-4.png 300w,\n/static/9d3ffadb4693960fa53446e9492efb91/0a47e/lru-cache-4.png 600w,\n/static/9d3ffadb4693960fa53446e9492efb91/00d43/lru-cache-4.png 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"2-get\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-get\" aria-label=\"2 get permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. get</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">get</code>의 경우에는 찾으려고하는 key의 value를 리턴해주면 되고, 만약 찾으려는 key값이 없는 경우에는 -1을 리턴해준다. 여기서 찾으려했던 값이 있었으면 그 값을 읽는 작업은 해당 메모리가 사용된거니까 앞쪽으로 위치해주는 작업을 해줘야한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 176.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"get\"\n        title=\"get\"\n        src=\"/static/9be165c109f14d620c80cb9fe8ee50ca/00d43/lru-cache-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9be165c109f14d620c80cb9fe8ee50ca/5a46d/lru-cache-5.png 300w,\n/static/9be165c109f14d620c80cb9fe8ee50ca/0a47e/lru-cache-5.png 600w,\n/static/9be165c109f14d620c80cb9fe8ee50ca/00d43/lru-cache-5.png 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h2 id=\"예제-이해하기\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%98%88%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9D%B4%ED%95%B4%ED%95%98%EA%B8%B0\" aria-label=\"예제 이해하기 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>예제 이해하기</h2>\n<p>그래서 예제를 이해하면 다음과 같다.\n<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1000px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 201.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"예제를 눈으로 정리\"\n        title=\"예제를 눈으로 정리\"\n        src=\"/static/2745e0af1024bc9192e5dc232686c462/00d43/lru-cache-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2745e0af1024bc9192e5dc232686c462/5a46d/lru-cache-2.png 300w,\n/static/2745e0af1024bc9192e5dc232686c462/0a47e/lru-cache-2.png 600w,\n/static/2745e0af1024bc9192e5dc232686c462/00d43/lru-cache-2.png 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>생성자에서 호출될때 용량이 얼마인지를 <code class=\"language-text\">this.capacity</code>에 저장하고 <code class=\"language-text\">this.keys</code>에 데이터들을 저장하도록 했다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"code\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code\" aria-label=\"code permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>code</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {number} capacity\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">LRUCache</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">capacity</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>keys <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>capacity <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> capacity<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">/** \n * @param {number} key\n * @return {number}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token class-name\">LRUCache</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">get</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">key</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">for</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> i<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>keys<span class=\"